caffsim
  • Reference

Create a dataset of the concentration-time curve

ConcTime will create a dataset of the concentration-time curve

ConcTime(Weight, Dose, N = 20)

Arguments

Weight

Body weight (kg)
Dose

Dose of single caffeine (mg)
N

The number of simulated subjects

Value

The dataset of concentration and time of simulated subjects

See also

http://asancpt.github.io/CaffeineEdison

Examples

ConcTime(Weight = 20, Dose = 200, N = 20)
